 a complete revenue forecast with trend analysis and seasonality."}],"url":"\/documentation\/businessmath\/buildingrevenuemodel","type":"topic"},"doc://com.jpurnell.BusinessMath/documentation/BusinessMath/TimeSeries":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.jpurnell.BusinessMath\/documentation\/BusinessMath\/TimeSeries","type":"topic","title":"Time Series Analysis","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/businessmath\/timeseries","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Work with temporal data using periods and time series containers."}],"role":"article"}}}